						               													<description>A card and board game where a wine novice can beat a connoisseur.&amp;#10;Worldwide Wines patented mode of play features &amp;quot;Region Cards&amp;quot;, which provide the game's strategic element and &amp;quot;Money Cards&amp;quot;, which educate players to the many aspects of wines of the world. &amp;#10;Players must collect and BUY certain combinations of &amp;quot;Region Cards&amp;quot;, which relate directly to the 106 wine regions on the game board map (Winning &amp;quot;R. Card&amp;quot; Combinations:3 stars/$24 Million each OR 4 wine bottles/$18 Million each OR 5 wine glasses/$14 Million each OR a &amp;quot;flush&amp;quot;).  &amp;#10;Over 300 &amp;quot;Money Cards&amp;quot; present players with a wide range of challenging questions and interesting facts on the wine regions, their wine styles and production methods.  The &amp;quot;Money Cards&amp;quot; also give OR take away the cash needed to buy strategic &amp;quot;Region Cards&amp;quot;.  WILD &amp;quot;Opportunity Cards&amp;quot; (included in the &amp;quot;Region Card&amp;quot; deck) give players the opportunity to buy owned &amp;quot;Region Cards&amp;quot; right out from under opponents.&amp;#10;All players have an equal chance of winning due to the &amp;quot;Region Card&amp;quot; strategy aspect.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
